  "prompt": "Can I change the nominee details in Atal Pension Yojana?",
  "response": "Yes, you can change the nominee details in Atal Pension Yojana (APY). Here's how:\n\n1. Offline Process:\n- Visit the bank branch where you opened the APY account\n- Fill out a nomination change form\n- Submit necessary documents like ID proof and original document\n- Bank will update your nominee details\n\n2. Online Process:\n- Log in to your APY account through the official portal\n- Navigate to nomination section\n- Update nominee details\n- Save the changes\n\nRequired Documents:\n- Identification proof\n- Address proof\n- Nominee's details\n- Relationship proof\n- Photograph\n\nImportant Points:\n- You can change nominee details multiple times\n- Nominee should be a family member\n- Nominee details can be updated at any time\n- No additional charges for nomination changes\n- Ensure all details are accurate\n\nRecommended Steps:\n- Visit your bank branch personally\n- Carry original documents\n- Verify details before submission\n- Keep a copy of nomination change form\n\nFor specific guidance, contact your bank or APY service provider directly.",
